articles.title: Five Americans freed in Iran prisoner swap land in US - BBC
articles.description: The four men and one woman return to the US after $6bn of frozen Iranian funds were released.
articles.content:
A plane carrying five Americans jailed in Iran for years has landed in the US after a controversial prisoner swap.
They touched down in Fort Belvoir, Virginia, just south of Washington DC on Tuesday… [+3834 chars]
